{"tid":970863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國官媒：中國已完成開發「炸彈之母」 威力僅次核武","createTime":"2019-01-06T07:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T03:37:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e3a01942489322c3d7a53e4589d4985fa12a66","tid":970863,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpoQzLfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpoQzLfF.png&h=d27e1209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國國營媒體《環球時報》指出，中國已經開發出威力僅次於核武的最強炸彈「炸彈之母」。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-06 10:41<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國國營媒體《環球時報》指出，中國已經開發出威力僅次於核武的最強炸彈「炸彈之母」（Mother Of All Bombs、MOAB）並已進行爆炸實驗，威力能夠輕易摧毀地面所有加固目標，且體型比美國的炸彈之母更小，可以由轟炸機載運。<br />\n<br />\n據《環球時報》報導，中國國營軍事公司「中國兵器工業集團（Norinco）」於官方網站放出新的宣傳影片，一架H-6K轟炸機將MOAB投在平原上，隨即爆發出巨大爆炸與黑煙。報導指出，一顆MOAB就有數噸重，轟炸機一次只能攜帶一顆，也是中國除了核武以外最強大的炸彈。而對於爆炸實驗進行的時間、地點與規模，報導則隻字未提。<br />\n<br />\n對於MOAB，北京軍事分析人士魏東旭指出，「炸彈之母」大約有5到6公尺長，巨大的爆炸可以輕易摧毀地面加固目標，如建築物、堡壘和防禦設施，還可以用來清除直升機部隊降落區域。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，美國於2017年4月13日曾在阿富汗東部投下「炸彈之母」，轟炸藏身地道的恐怖份子伊斯蘭國（IS）成員，殲滅至少94人。而魏東旭指出，中國的炸彈比美國的更小更輕，可以部署在轟-6K轟炸機上，但美國「炸彈之母」則必須由運輸機運載，體積更為巨大。魏東旭強調，轟炸機可以飛得比運輸機更快。中國的炸彈設計者在製造適合轟-6K的炸彈時，一定是考慮到這一點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2663278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2663278&d=X4%2FzfWi5cbJ7qy%2BCoL4PzROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1341079e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2663278&h=344f0d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2663278</a>"},{"pid":"4237dbc1b85620db221f0114f425c20d654283d9","tid":970863,"uid":37666,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:50:57.000Z","msg":"又吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08117032128f03f0ccb0770697230a0c25f7e845","tid":970863,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"成龍.jpg"},{"pid":"d26a2ddee133592cd78acd770ece5fc8700e6b64","tid":970863,"uid":33437,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"轟炸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，去到人地本土上空先算啦。"},{"pid":"dd87093e12103343d57febb99af886b4cd726ef0","tid":970863,"uid":136431,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"早幾年天津係試爆嚟？"},{"pid":"fdb772e54ee321c35b227d5b5cd14fc012dab1de","tid":970863,"uid":99209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"佢真係當人無防空咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d16badf8d1aac13116808726c87f59d9ad1f389","tid":970863,"uid":3302,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"可憐的小支那 每天都需要打飛機"},{"pid":"a39a19596d6f80e4e91d4167b25ced3cfe18cd6a","tid":970863,"uid":35667,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"都係用黎炸返中國人姐<br />\n洗唔洗搞咁多野"},{"pid":"b159f294b1ec0f4cd589173040999081e3028b6e","tid":970863,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"「一顆MOAB就有數噸重」<br />\n屌, 幾噸重, 幾噸TNT都好大威力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c5271ff43cfdee0653cc8ba428991f40b9738e","tid":970863,"uid":170019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"要黎自爆？"},{"pid":"46be024c2b9cc58a8360d068f19b9a9727589e6c","tid":970863,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"啲要有射出能力既野點解係母唔係父？"},{"pid":"99f044f1fa22df3c747ea80cf71fc1a2dfdc440f","tid":970863,"uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:08:04.000Z","msg":"中國只有炸彈是不會爆炸的"},{"pid":"927d9e784bae3d2c0ce79842e15cdb8359bf8e6d","tid":970863,"uid":8810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:10:57.000Z","msg":"我知，天津吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7236d9d5a7bf1e2d826d2950478b87db79d3cbfc","tid":970863,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"GBU-43/B大型空爆炸彈（英語：GBU-43/B <strong>M</strong>assive <strong>O</strong>rdnance <strong>A</strong>ir <strong>B</strong>last bomb，簡稱MOAB），俗稱炸彈之母（Mother Of All Bombs，取其簡寫也是「MOAB」之故），是一款超大型全球定位系統導引自由落體炸彈，由美國空軍研究實驗室研發，並由美國空軍實際配用。重量達21,600磅（約9,700公斤）、能產生相當於11噸黃色炸藥破壞力的MOAB主要用於破壞地下碉堡，引爆時破壞半徑可達1.6公里，並將半徑300至500公尺之內的氧氣燃燒到只有1/3濃度。GBU-43/B大型空爆炸彈因重量與體積關係，無法採由一般的戰機掛載，需由C-130「力士型」運輸機投擲。"},{"pid":"2a7af0e18771ca13c295cfd00a0487ff95d0cae7","tid":970863,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"「胖子」是至今為止歷史上第二次亦是最後一次對人類使用的核武器。它長10英呎八吋（3.25公尺），直徑五英呎（1.52公尺），重10,000磅（4,545公斤）。釋放的能量約相等於<span style=\"color: red;\">2.1萬公噸</span>的TNT烈性炸藥"},{"pid":"e298f86a72d9e5d9f77b63e2a98333aea9982798","tid":970863,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"巨型鑽地彈（英語：Massive Ordnance Penetrator，MOP，代號GBU-57A/B），是一種由美國空軍配備的大型精確制導鑽地炸彈，並為「碉堡剋星（英語：Bunker buster）」系列的新成員。因預估其威力可能超過俄羅斯的炸彈之父，故有媒體稱其為炸彈之祖。它的性能超越了目前最強大的掩體粉碎機&mdash;GBU-28，可能是其威力十倍以上，爆炸當量為俄羅斯炸彈之父的近3倍。"},{"pid":"e019d9c6b7451b10ae897ef71d951be83fbbcc55","tid":970863,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"繼續吹.gif"},{"pid":"5c7c568818368ad1ca190fdad5e6c3c5387c0dbf","tid":970863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb772e54ee321c35b227d5b5cd14fc012dab1de","tid":970863,"uid":99209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"佢真係當人無防空咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"佢當人無導彈"},{"pid":"5f56cff05e2eec10ee2a38637dfcc42db970664b","tid":970863,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"天津嗰粒都好勁啦喎"},{"pid":"9e8e761b7fe2f45d118e5bbb42e9abe328308360","tid":970863,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"共國肯定無能力開發<br />\n但見到華為點抄Cisco <br />\n我有D怕佢又係派間碟攞source 照copy"},{"pid":"de57dea550dfd598f3f085b9ad692e0c7191c640","tid":970863,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8e761b7fe2f45d118e5bbb42e9abe328308360","tid":970863,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"共國肯定無能力開發<br />\n但見到華為點抄Cisco <br />\n我有D怕佢又係派間碟攞source 照copy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"支那5g咁平<br />\n係因為唔駛r&amp;d成本"},{"pid":"6d9aef2b24f7b85e796b77d2593d03a3fc83180d","tid":970863,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02425cb9a5a1d81cba9a8896d24cd77faa05d988","tid":970863,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"出到第2島鍊當妳贏"},{"pid":"b9f7ca2b96e557142f96a3df744c7d77ae5f8dd3","tid":970863,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26a2ddee133592cd78acd770ece5fc8700e6b64","tid":970863,"uid":33437,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"轟炸機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，去到人地本土上空先算啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"係本土用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}